"Rediah": "Very well, I will now explain the \"Fashion Catalog\"."
"The Fashion Catalog is a feature that, among other things, allows you to browse through various different outfits."
"It contains various ways to filter and browse through a list of outfits made by other ARKS."
"Likewise, when you register your own \"Fashion\", other ARKS will be able to see it listed in this catalog."
"First, please to try to register your own Fashion in the Fashion Catalog."
"I look forward to what outfits you'll come up with."
